=========
 HEXJOIN 
=========
| 

about
-----
| 

:author:  Bart Thate <bthate@gmail.com>
:contact: IRCNET/#dunkbots
:distribution: core
:license: Public Domain
 
| 

description
-----------
| 

show ip and hostname from user joining a channel

| 


| 

commands
--------
| 

1) *hexjoin-cfg*

    :description: plugin configuration

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !hexjoin-cfg
        <output> options: channels=[] .. version="GOZERBOT 0.9"


2) *hexjoin-cfgsave*

    :description: save plugin configuration

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !hexjoin-cfgsave
        <output> config saved


3) *hexjoin-disable*

    :description: disable hexjoin in the channel this command is given in

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !hexjoin-disable
        <output> #test channel is not in channels list


4) *hexjoin-enable*

    :description: enable hexjoin in the channel the command is given in

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !hexjoin-enable
        <output> #test channel added


